    <item>
      <title>Version 1.0.3</title>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 13:38:41 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>4</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Opt1 1.0.3 release notes</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
           font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; padding: 12px; }
    h1, h2, h3 { margin-top: 1em; }
    code { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
           background: rgba(127,127,127,0.15); padding: 1px 4px;
           border-radius: 3px; }
    pre code { display: block; padding: 8px; }
    ul, ol { padding-left: 1.5em; }
    a { color: #0a84ff; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Opt1 1.0.3</h1>
<h2>What's new</h2>
<ul>
<li>Significantly improved Celtic Knot detection and solving.</li>
<li>Celtic knot no longer requires inversion for every puzzle.</li>
<li>Added an additional set of auto-triangulation points for Arc compasses.</li>
<li>Fixed lockbox and towers puzzles not detecting on larger screens.</li>
<li>Experimental support for RS3 in game UI scaling (tell us your scale in settings!).</li>
<li>The map in the compass window now zooms in on any calculated intersection.</li>
<li>Signficantly improved Scan clue detection.</li>
<li>Experimental support for scan clue pathing guidance.</li>
<li>Your choice to 'show all spots' in the compass window is now remembered.</li>
<li>Fixed some teleport locations showing in the wrong place.</li>
<li>Dig spots and teleport locations now show on the Arc map.</li>
<li>General improvements to matching of clue text.</li>
<li>Compass window is now moveable.</li>
<li>Scan window is now resizeable.</li>
<li>Aligned themeing across all windows.</li>
<li>Release notes should now display properly.</li>
</ul>
</body>
</html>
]]></description>
